title: Oliver's Real Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service organic fast food eatery with outlets in Australia NSW and VIC. Uses real food, natural ingredients. Its webpage lists separate menus for vegetarian, vegan, dairy-free, and gluten-free choices. This outlet is located in the Wyong Caltex Stopover and also features a grab-n-go selection of prepared food.
streetAddress: Caltex Stopover, M1 Freeway, Northbound, Caltex Stopover, M1 Freeway, Southbound
